# Example env file for analog-operator.
# All operator-app env vars must be prefixed with EXPO_PUBLIC_ to be accessible at runtime.
# No env vars are required for Phase 1 (TAC-112). Future entries:
#   EXPO_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL  — base URL for the analog-guest operator API (TAC-258)
#   EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL  — Supabase project URL (TAC-206)
#   EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY — Supabase anon key (TAC-206)
